{"tid":1443294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家用最大力輸出恐懼去各個平台","createTime":"2019-08-11T07:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:00:35.000Z","uid":279238,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb64536e67b7a64c00ce5bde87495a889939f44","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"依家每日資訊量太多，就算連登仔跟得貼都會有消化不良，更何況係一般大眾。不得不承認依家運動係出現疲態，亦有失焦，要知道香港人係金魚記憶，<span style=\"color: red;\">每星期不斷發生嘅相似資訊，無論係街坊食幾多TG、犠牲/被拉/受傷嘅手足，係咁大量資訊下都只會無奈地每日累積變成一個冷冰冰嘅數字</span><br />\n<br />\n依家已經係依場抗爭嘅第64日，除左講到口臭嘅5大訴求要繼續爭取，更<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">應該搵兩、三件依64日內發生嘅最大影響事件，易入口易消化易二元對立嘅事再去煲大佢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1）721元朗無差別斬人，無警時份，警黑合作<br />\n2）公安武警混入黑警，破壞一國兩制，挑起64恐懼<br />\n3）送中法案死灰復燃，再出現喺政府文獻，唔係壽終正寢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依3樣最易帶俾所謂嘅中間派、淺藍、立場唔穩定嘅淺黃最大恐懼，令佢地明白今次係無退路，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一般香港人係好撚蠢，唔會想去理解咁多背後前因後果，更係以感受行先多過對事實認知行先，運動前期點解會易掌握民意就係因為「二元」「正邪」「對錯」易理解，亦易挑起一般人廉價嘅同理心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n在此，麻煩大家，圍爐飛機post又好，笑9popo記者會post又好，都集中一兩個post就算，集中行動post之餘，更要集中做文宣、地區放送會，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">喺唔同平台送出簡單易入口嘅最大恐懼俾班中間、淺藍/黃</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地5年前已經輸到一敗塗地，我唔想今次再係咁樣<br />\n我求求大家！！！幫手輸出恐懼"},{"pid":"62d747df62850f46a5d630f390da2a6836bcb4df","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:44:55.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"df5269d5537358e6c3d422065abe5adbb67fc80b","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:45:32.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"332211c98c56e1418a7854db1fb6fc3126d46dd0","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:45:44.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"e828688f39656a3d19f56dc71d74cd6bba84b3db","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:46:05.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"05d323d06bb3de7149215477f2fc436f42831035","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:46:35.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"8e9b854f348c57b44d759ec90f48585d277ee88d","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"95b186c7e96df2ac862c409a780b685cc74652aa","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:47:55.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"80d8f6fc6e80d1f62d5a96fa04b4a9a17ecbe62b","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:47:59.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"e4c3bebd96c0b26677c3e82d2253c46535aa5a5b","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:48:06.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"dc438cc72b036a2e9d0983f1f27526e39a0a2308","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"b93ed94f9c74811210a4a8b362bf89e6db7454c2","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"我要吹風"},{"pid":"cb159c13e41fbf33b0c5400af5ca8b644a62ef5e","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:55:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3d735555917f4cedb9aaaa7658fbfcf0f3cef9c7","tid":1443294,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}